item.title: Logout Button
item.dc:creator: @johno2 johno2
item.description:
@johno2 wrote:

It depends, it could be server/client sided, if it’s server, open up client.java and search

logout

If it’s client sided, it could be in two places, GUI/Jframe.java or Client.java, once again search logout.

Hope this helps…
~Johno
